SUMMARY:Azure Community Hours - Modernize\, Build\, and Innovate on Azure
DESCRIPTION:Hello\n\n\n\n\nJoin&nbsp\;us for a focused Azure Community Hour
 s&nbsp\;series\, designed to help you accelerate your journey to modern\, 
 secure\, and scalable cloud solutions.\n\n\n\n\nEach session will focus on
  a different topic across Microsoft cloud technologies\, including:\n\n\n\
 n\n\nApplication and database modernization on Azure\n\nInfrastructure mig
 ration and hybrid cloud transformation\n\nSecurity\, governance\, and resi
 lience across cloud environments\n\nAI-powered applications and intelligen
 t agent scenarios\n\nModern data platform with Microsoft Fabric for analyt
 ics and data integration\n\nBusiness intelligence and data visualization w
 ith Power BI\n\n\n\n\n\nSessions include real-world guidance\, recommended
  architectures\, live demonstrations\, and practical insights from Microso
 ft experts.\n\n\n\n\nRegistration: Click here to complete the \nregistrati
 on\n\n\n\n\nWe look forward to having you join us!\n\n\n\n\n\n\nRegards\,\
 n\nRetail Azure Hours Event Team
